"""Raise ValueError if statistics cannot be gathered."""
with expected_protocol(ik.teledyne.MAUI, [init, 'PAST? CUST, P1'], [
    'CUST,P1,NULL,C3,AVG,UNDEF,HIGH,UNDEF,LAST,UNDEF,LOW,UNDEF,SIGMA,UNDEF,SWEEPS,0'
    ], sep='\n') as osc:
    with pytest.raises(ValueError):
        print(osc.measurement[0].statistics)
